some kind of monster.

799
00:37:22.990 --> 00:37:24.617
How dare they reject me!

800
00:37:24.659 --> 00:37:25.534
[squeaking]

801
00:37:25.576 --> 00:37:27.662
[all yelp]

802
00:37:27.703 --> 00:37:29.538
Well. if they don't
want you

803
