I'm a bad parent too.

834
00:38:42.111 --> 00:38:43.487
What?

835
00:38:43.529 --> 00:38:44.905
None of us know
what we're doing.

836
00:38:44.947 --> 00:38:46.907
We-We didn't even
want this. right?

837
00:38:46.949 --> 00:38:49.493
