H-Hi. there.

895
00:41:27.568 --> 00:41:29.987
[screeching]

896
00:41:30.029 --> 00:41:31.322
[exclaims]

897
00:41:35.493 --> 00:41:38.078
I'm too young to die.
I'm too young to die.

898
00:41:38.120 --> 00:41:39.914
I'm too young to die.

899
