and your whole family

936
00:43:14.341 --> 00:43:15.801
for all eternity.

937
00:43:15.843 --> 00:43:17.720
I can't wait to get installed.

938
00:43:17.761 --> 00:43:19.263
I'm going to look so hot.

939
00:43:19.305 --> 00:43:20.848
