1762
01:25:07.936 --> 01:25:08.978
I love you.

1763
01:25:15.276 --> 01:25:18.404
Okay. Bye.
[distorted] I love you.

1764
01:25:18.446 --> 01:25:20.573
[distorted] Okay. Bye.
