1765
01:25:20.615 --> 01:25:22.742
[ambassador speaking
alien language]

1766
01:25:22.784 --> 01:25:24.911
[distorted] Okay. Bye.
I love you.

1767
01:25:24.953 --> 01:25:26.621
[speaking alien language]

1768
01:25:31.835 --> 01:25:33.378
