being sent to us lately.

1785
01:27:08.306 --> 01:27:12.018
And it touches to
the deepest of human concerns.

1786
01:27:12.894 --> 01:27:13.937
Are we alone?

1787
01:29:30.907 --> 01:29:32.950
[radio static.
frequency changing]

1788
01:29:38.790 --> 01:29:41.209
[growling through radio]

1789
01:29:41.250 --> 01:29:43.461
